The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.ED. 

cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about Natural Language Processing (NLP) and its related fields. 

cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper discusses a search engine and a command-line tool for the resources. 

cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as NLP often involves the use of machine learning techniques. 

cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as NLP is a subfield of AI. 

cs.ED (Education) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper aims to facilitate NLP education and research.
